        "problem_eyebrow": "THE PROBLEM",
        "problem_title": "Your body is leaking performance — <em>and your jaw is why.</em>",
        "problem_body": "<p>When your jaw is out of alignment, your entire skeletal system compensates. You lose stability, burn extra energy fighting tension, and hit a performance ceiling that no supplement or training program can fix.</p>",
