    "collapsible_content_HA7hTA": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_bdwWYh": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is RS1?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>RS1 is Reviv's performance sport mouthguard — designed to align your jaw into its optimal neuromuscular position during athletic activity, improving strength, airflow, and full-body stability.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_b3Aq6U": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How is RS1 different from R1, R2, or R3?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>R1, R2, and R3 are designed for nighttime wear and dental recovery during sleep. RS1 is purpose-built for sport — with a design that keeps your airway open, provides a clenching surface for maximum output, and delivers results from your very first use.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_46p3KR": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does RS1 require any molding or fitting?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>No molding required. RS1 is ready to use straight out of the box — just fit it in and train.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_zVraUA": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will I feel a difference right away?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes. There's no break-in period. The jaw repositioning creates immediate changes in posture, stability, and breathing — stronger, more stable, better breathing from your very first use.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_wYPXBk": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What sports is RS1 designed for?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>RS1 is built for all high-intensity sports and training — powerlifting, bodybuilding, CrossFit, combat sports, team sports, and any activity where strength, stability, and oxygen intake matter. It also works for yoga, HIIT, tennis, golf, pickleball, hiking, and everyday active movement.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_zHYD8j": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I wear RS1 all day?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>RS1 is designed specifically for athletic use — gym sessions, classes, sport, and active daily movement. For all-day daytime wear in work, commuting, or social settings, we recommend the RD1 (RevivDay), which is engineered for comfort and ease of speech.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_RaENdr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I clean RS1?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Rinse with cold water before and after each use. For a deeper clean, use a soft toothbrush with mild soap. Avoid hot water — it can distort the shape. You can also use Repod for a thorough clean.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_VrBWRK": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the appliance made out of?",
            "icon": "check_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>RS1 is made from EVA + PP (Ethylene-Vinyl Acetate + Polypropylene) — BPA-free, food-grade, and FDA-compliant. Safe for daily athletic use.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
